{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/spring-restapi-03.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"crud-완성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#crud-%EC%99%84%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"crud 완성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CRUD 완성하기</h3>\n<p>게시판을 만들 때 가장 기본이 되는 4가지 기능이 CRUD 이다.<br>\nC(create) R(read) U(update) D(delete)<br>\n이 중 read를 이전 포스팅에서 다루어봤다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/29114/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/db3b6a4caa852ea9e24446d31d7da0d3/29114/1.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\nread와 마찬가지로 나머지 메소드도 구현해주었다.<br>\n각각의 메소드의 맞는 어노테이션을 달아주는 것이 포인트이다.\n<br><br>\n<h3 id=\"postman-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#postman-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"postman 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PostMan 설치하기</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/29114/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/efc66/2.png 885w,\n/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/c83ae/2.png 1180w,\n/static/289294c91b1e529890f249258f1167d9/29114/2.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\nAPI개발을 하다보면 여러 API주소들을 올바르게 작동하는지 확인해야하는데 브라우저로만 확인하기에는 다소 불편한 점이 있다.<br>\n이러한 과정을 쉽게 해결하기 위한 소프트웨어가 바로 POSTMAN이다.<br>\nPostMan 다운로드 : https://www.postman.com/https://www.postman.com/\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/29114/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/fcda8/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/6381474377649bacaf6bea2c900a78d5/29114/4.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n이렇게 프로토콜 방식과 주소를 입력하면 아래 결과를 확인할 수 있다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/29114/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/fcda8/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/fcda8/5.png 590w,\n/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/efc66/5.png 885w,\n/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/c83ae/5.png 1180w,\n/static/b8f5a0150fe8ff6e82322d44a6e49441/29114/5.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\nPost를 테스트해보기 위해 프로토콜 방식을 Post로 바꾸고 Query Params에 데이터를 넣어주면 자동으로 주소에 입력된다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 433px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3de05432023c5696411f5286c918ac0b/55fc0/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"pa